-- North Korea May Be Preparing for Nuclear Test, Mainichi Newspaper Reports
-- B y   G o   O n o m i t s u
-- 2010-11-18T23:53:54Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-18/north-korea-may-be-preparing-for-nuclear-test-mainichi-newspaper-reports.html
North Korea may be preparing for a
nuclear test in the northeastern area of the communist country,
the Mainichi newspaper said, citing unidentified Japanese
government officials.   Satellite images showed that tunnels used in previous
nuclear tests had been repaired and that new tunnels are now
being built, according to the Japanese newspaper.   To contact the reporter on this story:
Go Onomitsu in Tokyo at 
 gonomitsu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
